    "headline": "Brown-Forman and Pabst Brewing Company to Conclude Partnership for Flavored Malt Beverages in the U.S.",
    "summary": "LOUISVILLE, Ky., March 02, 2026--Brown-Forman Corporation (NYSE: BFA, BFB) and Pabst Brewing Company (\"Pabst\") today announced a mutual agreement to conclude their partnership related to flavored malt beverages (FMBs) within the United States. Effective July 7, 2026, Brown-Forman will assume management of the supply, sales, marketing, and distribution for these products.",
